	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P78_is_identified_by> "He was the 38th Coptic patriarch of Alexandria, the office which he held since 623 until his death.\n               In the Ethiopian tradition the writings attributed to \"Benjamin of Alexandria\" are rare, but can be found i. a. in\n             Bǝḥerāwi Kǝllǝlāwi Mangǝśti Tǝgrāy, ʿUrā Qirqos, UM-037 or in Hāymānota ʾabaw.  " .
